imdb.plot outline: In the 1800s, American politicians battle for supremacy as proponents of democracy in a new republic that culminates in a bitter pistol duel between political rivals, George Alexander Hamilton (Liam Lusk) and then sitting Vice President of the United States, Colonel Aaron Burr (Dean Dawson).
